Below is the **complete system-level breakdown** of:

# üî∑ LOGIC 3 ‚Äì Procurement Need Definition & Structuring

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£ PURPOSE OF THIS LOGIC

This logic converts:

> ‚ÄúWe need something‚Äù
> into
> A structured, standardized, auditable procurement request

It ensures:

* Clear specifications
* Comparable bids
* Fair evaluation
* Budget control
* Reduced ambiguity
* Legal defensibility

If this logic is weak ‚Üí evaluation becomes subjective, disputes increase, and procurement fails.

